================================================================================
Clean-room confirmation
================================================================================

The Apple Accessory Protocol (AAP) support in PodBridge is a clean-room
reimplementation built solely from publicly documented facts (PSM values,
opcodes, and packet-field descriptions). No source code from any GPL-licensed or
otherwise license-incompatible project, and no verbatim protocol-documentation
prose, has been copied into this repository. The governing clean-room rule lives
in docs/constitution.md; the evidence harvest is in docs/prior-art.md. MagicPairing
encryption is never defeated — only the cleartext AAP control channel is used.

